<h2>Your payslip is ready</h2>

<p>Hi {{employeeName}},</p>

<p>Your salary slip for <strong>{{periodLabel}}</strong> has been finalized and is now available in your portal.</p>

<div class="info-box">
  <p><strong>Summary</strong></p>
  <p>
    Period: {{periodLabel}}<br>
    Net payable: <strong>{{netPayable}}</strong>
  </p>
</div>

<p>You can download the PDF payslip from your portal:</p>

<a href="{{payslipUrl}}" class="button">View Payslip</a>

<p style="font-size: 14px; color: #718096;">Or copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
<a href="{{payslipUrl}}">{{payslipUrl}}</a></p>

<div class="divider"></div>

<p>If anything looks incorrect, please contact your HR team.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
<strong>{{companyName}}</strong></p>
